/**
 * AnimatedLogo — correct brain+chip SVG with Motion animations.
 *
 * The SVG uses filled paths (not strokes), so the animation strategy is:
 *  1. Each path fades + scales in on mount (staggered)
 *  2. A masked shimmer/light sweep passes over the whole logo on loop
 *  3. Individual paths pulse their opacity to simulate electricity
 *  4. The whole logo floats gently
 */
